# Performance and Stability Review Task List

- [ ] Explore the codebase structure and identify key modules (UI, Services, Native code).
- [ ] Identify potential threading issues (e.g., blocking the main UI thread).
- [ ] Review memory management (e.g., leaks, heavy allocations).
- [ ] Review JNI/Native code for stability and performance.
- [ ] Propose and implement fixes for discovered issues.
- [ ] Verify builds and run tests.
